description: Sonetel AB engages in the development and provision of Software-as-a-Service for external and internal communication services. The company is headquartered in Stockholm, Stockholm and currently employs 53 full-time employees. The company went IPO on 2017-04-12. The firm offers local telephone numbers, conference calls without Internet connection and any special software, as well as international business calls. The Company’s offer is delivered through the software platform, which makes delivery possible in a form of Software-As-A-Service. The firm sells services directly through its Internet site. The company also partners with Weebly in order to promote services. The Company’s markets comprise Europe, North America, Africa, Asia and Latin America. The Company’s subsidiaries are Sonetel Software Services private ltd in India and The Global Entrepreneur Ubique AB in Sweden.
name: Sonetel AB (publ)
